{"tid":2515150,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[#Mon#Monitor] 電腦螢幕集中討論#63","createTime":"2021-05-03T18:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T22:40:25.000Z","uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5a889557c5877175b690e64a9fcc21b52f7b1fe6","tid":2515150,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T18:25:44.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">Newegg/AOC/Philips為中資公司</span><br />\n<br />\n不想自行做功課, 只求快想省時間,<br />\n對研究螢幕一點興趣都沒有的求推薦文,<br />\n個人看到一律會跳過<br />\n<br />\n總之, 推薦文的話, 就請期待其他網友幫忙吧<br />\n<br />\n除非有看到做功課做很多的香港網友, 問出有水準的問題<br />\n個人也許還會回答, 但應該只會是極少數.<br />\n偶而才來看看, 基本上也不用期待<br />\n<br />\n香港的螢幕規格表暫時還有在幫忙更新,<br />\n<br />\n但現在也該是時候出現下一個,<br />\n像多鮫魚巴打一樣的香港人物了吧..<br />\n<br />\n星河電腦螢幕資訊分享站<br />\n<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/view/twmonitors/首頁\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fview%2Ftwmonitors%2F%E9%A6%96%E9%A0%81&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=cfc8f4f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/view/twmonitors/首頁</a><br />\n<br />\n多多查看網站學習做功課, 親自思考自己要買什麼樣的產品.<br />\n<br />\n其中幾個表格就算香港地區也應有相當的參考度<br />\n<br />\n香港版144HZ/21:9/2K/4K螢幕規格表連結<br />\n<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/view/twmonitors/查看表格/香港地區專頁\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fview%2Ftwmonitors%2F%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%80%E5%B0%88%E9%A0%81&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=fd2b7c5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/view/twmonitors/查看表格/香港地區專頁</a><br />\n<br />\n香港地區販賣的螢幕產品規格表, 有對應的價錢方便比價<br />\n<br />\n2019同步總評表<br />\n<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/view/twmonitors/年度大賞/2019總評表不定期更新\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fview%2Ftwmonitors%2F%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E5%A4%A7%E8%B3%9E%2F2019%E7%B8%BD%E8%A9%95%E8%A1%A8%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%9A%E6%9C%9F%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=402ae37b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/view/twmonitors/年度大賞/2019總評表不定期更新</a><br />\n<br />\n無限預算推薦表<br />\n<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/view/twmonitors/查看表格/無限預算推薦表\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fview%2Ftwmonitors%2F%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC%2F%E7%84%A1%E9%99%90%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%8E%A8%E8%96%A6%E8%A1%A8&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=59390119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/view/twmonitors/查看表格/無限預算推薦表</a><br />\n<br />\n低價高CP推薦表<br />\n<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/view/twmonitors/查看表格/低價高cp推薦表\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fview%2Ftwmonitors%2F%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC%2F%E4%BD%8E%E5%83%B9%E9%AB%98cp%E6%8E%A8%E8%96%A6%E8%A1%A8&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=b0ef7b32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/view/twmonitors/查看表格/低價高cp推薦表</a><br />\n<br />\n多鮫魚電腦螢幕知識分享站<br />\n<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/view/monitor101/首頁\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fview%2Fmonitor101%2F%E9%A6%96%E9%A0%81&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=e32abab1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/view/monitor101/首頁</a><br />\n<br />\n這個則是多鮫魚巴打(1~10帖作者)整理出來的網頁<br />\n有推薦清單跟一些知識部分, 也具有參考性.<br />\n<br />\n香港螢幕報價表<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/dN1MKA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FdN1MKA&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=fda31913\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/dN1MKA</a><br />\n<br />\n為了讓更多港友知道最新價格與價錢透明化, 多鮫魚巴打建議有查到價錢報價的, 寫到共用表格上, 讓港友都能進行更詳細的價錢比較<br />\n(據說Price hk價錢更新過慢)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBest 144hz-240hz Monitors (NCX's Ranking)<br />\n<a href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20170926175434/http://wecravegamestoo.com:80/forums/monitor-reviews-discussion/15713-best-144hz-240hz-monitors.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20170926175434%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwecravegamestoo.com%3A80%2Fforums%2Fmonitor-reviews-discussion%2F15713-best-144hz-240hz-monitors.html&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=4aaf1706\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://web.archive.org/web/20170926175434/http://wecravegamestoo.com:80/forums/monitor-reviews-discussion/15713-best-144hz-240hz-monitors.html</a><br />\n<br />\n英文不錯也可以去看看NCX之前的144Hz排行帖內容<br />\n另外推薦港友多多參考<br />\n<br />\n&quot;香港格價網&quot; Price HK的價錢還有店家資訊<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.price.com.hk/category.php?c=100024\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.price.com.hk%2Fcategory.php%3Fc%3D100024&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=34cc4f27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.price.com.hk/category.php?c=100024</a><br />\n<br />\n想買哪一款螢幕不知道哪裡有在賣, 有沒有現貨,<br />\n可以查看這個網站, 然後打電話聯絡店家進行詢問.<br />\n<br />\n基本注意事項<br />\n1. IPS/VA/TN差距為何很重要, 請自行爬文研究.<br />\n2. 4K遊戲, 顯示卡2080或以上才有資格跑, 顯示卡差只能降解析度跑<br />\n3. 看影片, 沒有50%時間以上都玩競技型(FPS/賽車)遊戲, TN直接淘汰, 選VA or IPS<br />\n4. PS4/PS4 Pro/Switch不支援2k輸出, 只支援FHD, 顯示到2k螢幕會需放大較模糊些, 優先選擇FHD產品<br />\n5. 4K + TN螢幕, 全部都是垃圾, 不需考慮.<br />\n6. TN + 60hz產品,不具參考價值.<br />\n7. HDR10=格式，HDR400-1400=認證。目前主流HDR資源都係HDR10格式 市面上HDR MON HDR10性能有高有低 所以VESA 搞左個displayHDR認證<br />\n分為HDR400/500/600/1000/1400 另外仲有UHD premium認證 大概等同HDR1000 冇任何認證會只標支援HDR10"},{"pid":"35a7e67f3033ad073d70cf165868e2e7ce02af71","tid":2515150,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T18:26:33.000Z","msg":"建議 LIST<br />\n2K 144HZ VG27AQL1A / XG279Q<br />\n4K 60HZ VG289Q<br />\n4K 144HZ XG27UQ / 27GN950-B<br />\n<br />\nDisplay Port 1.4 線<br />\n無認證 但出到4K144HZ<br />\n<a href=\"https://shop.hornington.com/products/j5create-jdc43-8k-displayport-cable-2m\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshop.hornington.com%2Fproducts%2Fj5create-jdc43-8k-displayport-cable-2m&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=d7e7467a\" target=\"_blank\">https://shop.hornington.com/products/j5create-jdc43-8k-displayport-cable-2m</a>"},{"pid":"e46c2183c47bc81f984aa4fd970e9692ecd0e6a2","tid":2515150,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T18:28:02.000Z","msg":"建議 LIST<br />\n2K 144HZ VG27AQL1A / XG279Q<br />\n4K 60HZ VG289Q<br />\n4K 144HZ XG27UQ / 27GN950-B<br />\n<br />\n有HDMI 2.1 新MOON推出<br />\n請留意新消息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDisplay Port 1.4 線<br />\n無認證 但出到4K144HZ<br />\n<a href=\"https://shop.hornington.com/products/j5create-jdc43-8k-displayport-cable-2m\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshop.hornington.com%2Fproducts%2Fj5create-jdc43-8k-displayport-cable-2m&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=d7e7467a\" target=\"_blank\">https://shop.hornington.com/products/j5create-jdc43-8k-displayport-cable-2m</a>"},{"pid":"528f0bf193d8ee3ea555a9fc50f210fe0afc424a","tid":2515150,"uid":159409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T22:40:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />輕輕一推"}],"pinned":{"pid":"e46c2183c47bc81f984aa4fd970e9692ecd0e6a2","tid":2515150,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T18:28:02.000Z","msg":"建議 LIST<br />\n2K 144HZ VG27AQL1A / XG279Q<br />\n4K 60HZ VG289Q<br />\n4K 144HZ XG27UQ / 27GN950-B<br />\n<br />\n有HDMI 2.1 新MOON推出<br />\n請留意新消息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDisplay Port 1.4 線<br />\n無認證 但出到4K144HZ<br />\n<a href=\"https://shop.hornington.com/products/j5create-jdc43-8k-displayport-cable-2m\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshop.hornington.com%2Fproducts%2Fj5create-jdc43-8k-displayport-cable-2m&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=d7e7467a\" target=\"_blank\">https://shop.hornington.com/products/j5create-jdc43-8k-displayport-cable-2m</a>"}}